{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a 3-column comparison table with 4 rows. Column 1: Attribute labels with emojis. Column 2: [BRAND_NAME] (hero column, highlighted). Columns 3-4: Two competitor categories.
    STRUCTURE:
    Row 1: Calories (📦 emoji)
    Row 2: [KEY_INGREDIENT] like Protein (💪 emoji)
    Row 3: [UNDESIRABLE] like Sugar (🔪 emoji)
    Row 4: Price (💰 emoji)
    STYLING:
    Hero Column (center): Light pastel background matching brand, rounded border 20px radius, subtle shadow, bold numbers.
    Competitor Columns: White background, no borders, regular font, muted gray text.
    Attribute Labels: Left-aligned, semi-bold.
    DATA FORMAT:
    Brand column: Exact values with context ("120cal in 2 scoops", "20g in 2 scoops", "0g")
    Competitor columns: Ranges or typical values ("150-400cal", "2-12g", "20-50g")
    Price row: Use emoji faces (😊 for good value, ☹️ for expensive) OR actual prices
    VARIABLES TO FILL:
    [BRAND_NAME] = Product name
    [KEY_INGREDIENT] = Main benefit (Protein/Collagen/Active%)
    [UNDESIRABLE] = What to avoid (Sugar/Parabens/Chemicals)
    [COMPETITOR_1_NAME] = Category like "Mainstream Coffees"
    [COMPETITOR_2_NAME] = Category like "Protein Drinks"
    GOAL: Make brand column visually dominant, competitors fade into background. Show brand superiority through better numbers and portion transparency, i want the table design to be compact and fit all within mobile max width.
    
    and on desktop has adjustable options, instead of emoji let me upload icons
    
    and add ability to add more rows
    
    and add abilibty to add check mark or X mark on the coulm 1 , 2 , 3 values if i want
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-comparison-table-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding }}px 20px;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    overflow-x: visible;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__table-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: separate;
    border-spacing: 0;
    table-layout: fixed;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} th {
    padding: {{ block.settings.cell_padding }}px {{ block.settings.cell_padding | times: 0.5 }}px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.header_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-bottom: 2px solid {{ block.settings.border_color }};
    word-wrap: break-word;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} th:first-child {
    text-align: left;
    width: 30%;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} th:nth-child(2) {
    width: 28%;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} th:nth-child(3),
  .ai-comparison-table__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} th:nth-child(4) {
    width: 21%;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} .ai-comparison-table__hero-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.hero_bg_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.hero_border_radius }}px {{ block.settings.hero_border_radius }}px 0 0;
    box-shadow: {{ block.settings.hero_shadow_x }}px {{ block.settings.hero_shadow_y }}px {{ block.settings.hero_shadow_blur }}px {{ block.settings.hero_shadow_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.hero_text_color }};
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} .ai-comparison-table__competitor-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.competitor_bg_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.competitor_text_color }};
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__body-{{ ai_gen_id }} td {
    padding: {{ block.settings.cell_padding }}px {{ block.settings.cell_padding | times: 0.5 }}px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid {{ block.settings.border_color }};
    word-wrap: break-word;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.label_font_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.label_text_color }};
    line-height: 1.3;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__hero-cell-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.hero_bg_color }};
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.hero_value_font_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.hero_text_color }};
    box-shadow: {{ block.settings.hero_shadow_x }}px {{ block.settings.hero_shadow_y }}px {{ block.settings.hero_shadow_blur }}px {{ block.settings.hero_shadow_color }};
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__body-{{ ai_gen_id }} tr:last-child .ai-comparison-table__hero-cell-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    border-radius: 0 0 {{ block.settings.hero_border_radius }}px {{ block.settings.hero_border_radius }}px;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__competitor-cell-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.competitor_bg_color }};
    text-align: center;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.competitor_value_font_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.competitor_text_color }};
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__value-context-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.context_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: 400;
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-top: 2px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__check-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    width: {{ block.settings.check_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.check_size }}px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__check-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__check-yes-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.check_color }};
  }

  .ai-comparison-table__check-no-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.x_color }};
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-comparison-table-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 20px 12px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-table__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} th {
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 10px 4px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-table__body-{{ ai_gen_id }} td {
      padding: 10px 4px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-table__label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 11px;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-table__icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-table__hero-cell-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-table__competitor-cell-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-table__value-context-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 9px;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .ai-comparison-table__check-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: {{ block.settings.check_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
      height: {{ block.settings.check_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-comparison-table-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      max-width: {{ block.settings.desktop_max_width }}px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .ai-comparison-table__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} th:first-child {
      width: {{ block.settings.desktop_label_width }}%;
    }

    .ai-comparison-table__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} th:nth-child(2) {
      width: {{ block.settings.desktop_hero_width }}%;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-comparison-table-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-comparison-table__wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <table class="ai-comparison-table__table-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <thead class="ai-comparison-table__header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        <tr>
          <th></th>
          <th class="ai-comparison-table__hero-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.brand_name }}</th>
          <th class="ai-comparison-table__competitor-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.competitor_1_name }}</th>
          <th class="ai-comparison-table__competitor-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.competitor_2_name }}</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="ai-comparison-table__body-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% for i in (1..10) %}
          {% liquid
            assign enabled_key = 'row_' | append: i | append: '_enabled'
            assign icon_key = 'row_' | append: i | append: '_icon'
            assign label_key = 'row_' | append: i | append: '_label'
            assign brand_type_key = 'row_' | append: i | append: '_brand_type'
            assign brand_value_key = 'row_' | append: i | append: '_brand_value'
            assign brand_context_key = 'row_' | append: i | append: '_brand_context'
            assign comp1_type_key = 'row_' | append: i | append: '_comp1_type'
            assign comp1_value_key = 'row_' | append: i | append: '_comp1_value'
            assign comp2_type_key = 'row_' | append: i | append: '_comp2_type'
            assign comp2_value_key = 'row_' | append: i | append: '_comp2_value'

            assign enabled = block.settings[enabled_key]
            assign icon = block.settings[icon_key]
            assign label = block.settings[label_key]
            assign brand_type = block.settings[brand_type_key]
            assign brand_value = block.settings[brand_value_key]
            assign brand_context = block.settings[brand_context_key]
            assign comp1_type = block.settings[comp1_type_key]
            assign comp1_value = block.settings[comp1_value_key]
            assign comp2_type = block.settings[comp2_type_key]
            assign comp2_value = block.settings[comp2_value_key]
          %}

          {% if enabled %}
            <tr>
              <td class="ai-comparison-table__label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if icon != blank %}
                  <img 
                    src="{{ icon | image_url: width: 100 }}" 
                    alt="{{ label }}"
                    class="ai-comparison-table__icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                    width="100"
                    height="100"
                    loading="lazy"
                  >
                {% endif %}
                <span>{{ label }}</span>
              </td>
              <td class="ai-comparison-table__hero-cell-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if brand_type == 'check' %}
                  <span class="ai-comparison-table__check-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-comparison-table__check-yes-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                {% elsif brand_type == 'x' %}
                  <span class="ai-comparison-table__check-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-comparison-table__check-no-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                      <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                {% else %}
                  {{ brand_value }}
                  {% if brand_context != blank %}
                    <span class="ai-comparison-table__value-context-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ brand_context }}</span>
                  {% endif %}
                {% endif %}
              </td>
              <td class="ai-comparison-table__competitor-cell-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if comp1_type == 'check' %}
                  <span class="ai-comparison-table__check-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-comparison-table__check-yes-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                {% elsif comp1_type == 'x' %}
                  <span class="ai-comparison-table__check-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-comparison-table__check-no-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                      <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                {% else %}
                  {{ comp1_value }}
                {% endif %}
              </td>
              <td class="ai-comparison-table__competitor-cell-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if comp2_type == 'check' %}
                  <span class="ai-comparison-table__check-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-comparison-table__check-yes-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                {% elsif comp2_type == 'x' %}
                  <span class="ai-comparison-table__check-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-comparison-table__check-no-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                      <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                      <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                {% else %}
                  {{ comp2_value }}
                {% endif %}
              </td>
            </tr>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

